Class VertexMergerGroup

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.tinfour.common.Vertex

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ISamplePoint
    public class VertexMergerGroup
extends Vertex
    A synthetic vertex used to handle cases when multiple vertices occupy coincident locations.
